          "Linear part: $\\sum_{k=1}^{n}s_k u=u\\sum_{k=1}^{n}(-1)^k$, which is $0$ ($n$ even) or $-u$ ($n$ odd); either way it $\\to 0$ as $n\\to\\infty$.",
