          "Since $N_n\\in\\mathbb Z$, $\\sin(\\pi N_n)=0$ and $\\cos(\\pi N_n)=(-1)^{N_n}=+1$ (as $N_n$ is even). Thus $$\\sin(\\pi a^n)=-\\sin(\\pi b^n).$$",
