          "Expanding $4-4\\varepsilon_n+\\varepsilon_n^2=4-\\varepsilon_{n-1}$ gives the exact gap recursion $$\\varepsilon_{n-1}=4\\varepsilon_n-\\varepsilon_n^2=4\\varepsilon_n\\Big(1-\\tfrac{\\varepsilon_n}{4}\\Big).$$",
